00:09:08.783 --> 00:09:10.017 position:27% line:89% align:start
would seem silly.

00:09:10.151 --> 00:09:12.586 position:19% line:83% align:start
If they all got toasty,
they'd be happy.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.155 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't you think?

00:09:14.855 --> 00:09:16.891 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[SHY] Um, Pepesha?
-Huh?

00:09:18.626 --> 00:09:20.361 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why are you in my bedroom?

00:09:20.694 --> 00:09:21.929 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:09:23.597 --> 00:09:24.865 position:38% line:89% align:start
I forgot!

00:09:24.999 --> 00:09:26.067 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm?!

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:28.202 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh, but don't worry
your pretty little head!

00:09:28.335 --> 00:09:29.937 position:21% line:83% align:start
I may have forgotten
why I'm here,

00:09:30.071 --> 00:09:32.206 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I do remember
what you need to do!

00:09:32.339 --> 00:09:33.340 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sighing]

00:09:33.841 --> 00:09:35.776 position:27% line:89% align:start
Now Teru? Listen!

00:09:35.943 --> 00:09:38.345 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Open your ears!
-[squirming]

00:09:38.547 --> 00:09:39.914 position:27% line:83% align:start
We can't just go
and make everyone

00:09:40.047 --> 00:09:42.049 position:10% line:89% align:start
