what you're saying!

00:10:03.437 --> 00:10:04.638 position:16% line:89% align:start
Are you making fun of me?

00:10:04.772 --> 00:10:06.173 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, no, that's not it at all,

00:10:06.307 --> 00:10:08.375 position:30% line:83% align:start
what I'm trying
to say is, uh...

00:10:09.043 --> 00:10:11.245 position:24% line:83% align:start
