in this world,

00:10:11.378 --> 00:10:13.080 position:13% line:89% align:start
who can save every person.

00:10:13.214 --> 00:10:14.415 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:14.549 --> 00:10:17.184 position:16% line:83% align:start
But still, you can't stop
just 'cause you're scared.

00:10:18.319 --> 00:10:21.122 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hold on tight to the lives
you were able to save,

00:10:21.255 --> 00:10:23.357 position:24% line:83% align:start
and carry with you
the ones you couldn't

00:10:23.491 --> 00:10:24.859 position:16% line:89% align:start
and keep moving forward.

00:10:24.992 --> 00:10:27.128 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's what heroes do, right?

00:10:28.195 --> 00:10:29.096 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:10:29.230 --> 00:10:30.498 position:33% line:89% align:start
But, Pepesha,

00:10:30.631 --> 00:10:32.266 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm not like you, I can't--

00:10:32.399 --> 00:10:33.502 position:30% line:89% align:start
[phone chiming]

00:10:33.634 --> 00:10:34.902 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm?!

00:10:35.537 --> 00:10:36.804 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yes, what is it?

00:10:36.937 --> 00:10:39.039 position:13% line:83% align:start
Huh?! There's an emergency
in Petersburg?

00:10:39.173 --> 00:10:41.775 position:16% line:83% align:start
Aw, but I wanted to spend
more time with little Teru!

00:10:41.909 --> 00:10:43.844 position:13% line:89% align:start
Okay, okay, I'm on my way!

00:10:44.478 --> 00:10:45.713 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, Teru!

00:10:45.846 --> 00:10:47.516 position:19% line:83% align:start
I really wish we could
chat some more.

00:10:47.648 --> 00:10:50.619 position:10% line:83% align:start
But I'll be back as soon as I
remember why I came here.

00:10:50.751 --> 00:10:52.419 position:33% line:89% align:start
Bye-bye! Woo!

00:10:52.554 --> 00:10:54.255 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, uh, sure.

00:10:54.388 --> 00:10:55.890 position:30% line:89% align:start
See you later.

00:10:57.858 --> 00:10:59.727 position:16% line:89% align:start
