00:11:05.366 --> 00:11:08.202 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
No hero can save every person.

00:11:09.770 --> 00:11:12.273 position:24% line:83% align:start
If I start thinking
about it that way,

00:11:12.673 --> 00:11:14.708 position:7% line:89% align:start
