00:11:20.615 --> 00:11:21.650 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE STUDENT 1D]
I'm stumped.

00:11:21.782 --> 00:11:23.217 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you want
to watch tonight?

00:11:23.417 --> 00:11:26.187 position:19% line:83% align:start
[SHY] What did she mean
I should "carry" them with me?

00:11:26.655 --> 00:11:29.056 position:13% line:89% align:start
Like, take responsibility?

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:30.457 position:33% line:89% align:start
In that case,

00:11:30.592 --> 00:11:32.159 position:21% line:83% align:start
how's that different
from what I'm doing now?

00:11:32.293 --> 00:11:34.195 position:19% line:83% align:start
[MALE STUDENT 1D] Hey,
you know that Hero Shy?

00:11:34.328 --> 00:11:35.296 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:11:35.429 --> 00:11:36.897 position:27% line:83% align:start
