00:12:53.508 --> 00:12:54.542 position:44% line:89% align:start
Why?

00:12:55.142 --> 00:12:57.077 position:30% line:89% align:start
I have to help.

00:12:57.478 --> 00:12:59.213 position:24% line:89% align:start
If I don't, then...

00:13:00.615 --> 00:13:02.416 position:21% line:83% align:start
