00:13:07.788 --> 00:13:08.922 position:41% line:83% align:start
[DAIGO]
I don't care about that!

00:13:09.056 --> 00:13:11.292 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's my duty to go
and save them!

00:13:12.259 --> 00:13:13.994 position:21% line:89% align:start
Because the Hero Shy,

00:13:14.194 --> 00:13:16.163 position:19% line:89% align:start
saved me and my sister!

00:13:16.765 --> 00:13:18.767 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now it's my turn
to save everyone!

00:13:19.300 --> 00:13:20.602 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
A little boy?

00:13:20.735 --> 00:13:23.505 position:33% line:83% align:start
Listen, kid!
Fire's really scary, you know!

00:13:23.638 --> 00:13:24.773 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah, but I wanna defeat

00:13:24.905 --> 00:13:26.440 position:27% line:83% align:start
