and protect people!

00:13:26.574 --> 00:13:28.976 position:10% line:83% align:start
Because that's what it means
to be a hero!

00:13:29.276 --> 00:13:29.977 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

00:13:30.110 --> 00:13:31.278 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exploding]

