The building's coming apart!

00:13:39.654 --> 00:13:40.888 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashing]

00:13:42.356 --> 00:13:44.258 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MALE SPECTATOR 1B] No! Did
that little boy get crushed?

00:13:44.391 --> 00:13:45.859 position:24% line:83% align:start
[MALE SPECTATOR 1C]
Is he okay?

00:13:46.026 --> 00:13:47.629 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey, you all right?

00:13:47.762 --> 00:13:48.962 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:13:49.096 --> 00:13:50.030 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MALE FIREFIGHTER 1B]
Everyone, please!

00:13:50.164 --> 00:13:51.165 position:10% line:89% align:start
Stand clear of the building!

00:13:51.298 --> 00:13:53.200 position:7% line:89% align:start
Doesn't seem like you got hurt.

00:13:53.467 --> 00:13:54.502 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's good.

00:13:56.070 --> 00:13:59.173 position:27% line:83% align:start
Shrimpy, there's
a huge fire at T-1 Hotel.

00:13:59.507 --> 00:14:00.508 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

