I'm going inside.

00:14:05.647 --> 00:14:06.648 position:41% line:89% align:start
Miss...

00:14:06.947 --> 00:14:08.248 position:35% line:89% align:start
are you...?

00:14:08.817 --> 00:14:10.552 position:16% line:89% align:start
You were right, you know.

00:14:11.185 --> 00:14:13.354 position:24% line:83% align:start
About what it means
to be a Hero.

00:14:15.322 --> 00:14:17.024 position:41% line:83% align:start
