00:14:21.796 --> 00:14:24.566 position:7% line:89% align:start
But even so, I'll keep moving.

00:14:25.032 --> 00:14:27.034 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll push past the fear.

00:14:29.036 --> 00:14:30.270 position:35% line:89% align:start
Because...

00:14:30.404 --> 00:14:31.405 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clanging]

00:14:31.539 --> 00:14:32.574 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:14:37.512 --> 00:14:38.680 position:35% line:89% align:start
