00:14:48.288 --> 00:14:49.022 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm!

00:14:49.156 --> 00:14:50.825 position:35% line:83% align:start
[grunting]
Hey, kid,

00:14:50.958 --> 00:14:52.359 position:24% line:89% align:start
are you all right?

00:14:52.660 --> 00:14:53.894 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:14:55.229 --> 00:14:57.297 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
I'm so stupid, stupid, stupid!

00:14:57.431 --> 00:14:59.366 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm the biggest idiot
in the universe!

00:14:59.534 --> 00:15:01.101 position:33% line:83% align:start
I was so busy
worrying about myself

00:15:01.235 --> 00:15:02.903 position:13% line:89% align:start
