-[crying]
-[gasps]

00:15:38.005 --> 00:15:38.907 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:39.039 --> 00:15:40.140 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, can you hear me?

00:15:40.274 --> 00:15:41.676 position:24% line:89% align:start
Are you all right?

00:15:43.210 --> 00:15:45.245 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
She doesn't have a pulse!

00:15:45.814 --> 00:15:47.014 position:24% line:89% align:start
