as soon as I can!

00:16:02.931 --> 00:16:04.331 position:27% line:89% align:start
If I can do that,

00:16:05.098 --> 00:16:07.000 position:19% line:89% align:start
I know she'll be okay!

00:16:07.635 --> 00:16:08.670 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashing]

00:16:09.938 --> 00:16:11.171 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:16:22.216 --> 00:16:23.984 position:33% line:89% align:start
I promise...

00:16:24.652 --> 00:16:26.320 position:24% line:89% align:start
that I'll save her!

