00:16:32.125 --> 00:16:33.595 position:27% line:89% align:start
I won't make it!

00:16:36.831 --> 00:16:39.366 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT] Good to see you've
got your spirit back, Teru.

00:16:39.500 --> 00:16:40.467 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:16:40.602 --> 00:16:42.637 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

