00:16:45.940 --> 00:16:47.174 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
Pepesha?

00:16:47.876 --> 00:16:49.076 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Welcome back!

00:16:49.376 --> 00:16:52.112 position:21% line:83% align:start
