[indistinct chatter]

00:17:00.622 --> 00:17:02.222 position:21% line:83% align:start
[MALE FIREFIGHTER 1A]
Evacuations are complete,

00:17:02.356 --> 00:17:04.024 position:13% line:89% align:start
