00:19:11.385 --> 00:19:14.622 position:13% line:83% align:start
the real reason that I came
to see you the other day, Teru!

00:19:15.056 --> 00:19:16.289 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:19:17.224 --> 00:19:18.660 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

