in two seconds flat!

00:19:36.276 --> 00:19:38.980 position:13% line:89% align:start
Ahem! Where exactly are we?

00:19:39.147 --> 00:19:40.280 position:19% line:89% align:start
This place is basically

00:19:40.414 --> 00:19:42.517 position:27% line:83% align:start
a secret hideout
for Heroes like us.

00:19:43.685 --> 00:19:45.953 position:38% line:83% align:start
[UNILORD]
It's a pleasure to meet you,

00:19:46.087 --> 00:19:47.889 position:27% line:89% align:start
Teru Momijiyama.

00:19:48.156 --> 00:19:49.189 position:35% line:89% align:start
Or rather,

00:19:49.557 --> 00:19:51.859 position:24% line:89% align:start
the Hero of Japan.

00:19:52.627 --> 00:19:53.861 position:44% line:89% align:start
Shy.

00:19:55.429 --> 00:19:58.032 position:19% line:83% align:start
