since you became a Hero.

00:19:58.599 --> 00:20:01.703 position:13% line:83% align:start
I truly wish that you and I
could have met sooner.

00:20:02.436 --> 00:20:03.871 position:30% line:89% align:start
But no matter.

00:20:05.973 --> 00:20:07.542 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Hold on.
-[gasps]

00:20:07.675 --> 00:20:08.710 position:44% line:89% align:start
Shy?

00:20:08.910 --> 00:20:10.310 position:16% line:89% align:start
Are you able to hear me?

00:20:10.444 --> 00:20:11.679 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:20:15.348 --> 00:20:16.784 position:16% line:89% align:start
Is something the matter?

00:20:16.918 --> 00:20:18.619 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, she's shy, get it?

00:20:19.787 --> 00:20:22.355 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
She's just so beautiful!

00:20:22.924 --> 00:20:25.225 position:16% line:89% align:start
Uh, and who might you be?

00:20:25.660 --> 00:20:27.360 position:16% line:89% align:start
I am the one charged with

00:20:27.494 --> 00:20:29.997 position:27% line:83% align:start
watching over all
the Heroes of Earth.

00:20:30.363 --> 00:20:33.067 position:10% line:89% align:start
The Heavenly Empress Unilord.

00:20:33.201 --> 00:20:34.468 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
Empress?

00:20:34.602 --> 00:20:37.004 position:21% line:83% align:start
But there is no need
for such formality.

00:20:37.337 --> 00:20:38.305 position:41% line:89% align:start
Please,

00:20:38.438 --> 00:20:40.208 position:7% line:89% align:start
