a different name.

00:20:42.409 --> 00:20:43.644 position:38% line:89% align:start
Call me,

00:20:43.778 --> 00:20:44.846 position:38% line:89% align:start
"Eunnie."

00:20:46.047 --> 00:20:47.081 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:20:47.481 --> 00:20:48.716 position:41% line:89% align:start
