00:20:59.493 --> 00:21:01.996 position:24% line:83% align:start
I suppose I'll get
straight to the point, then.

00:21:03.531 --> 00:21:05.432 position:19% line:89% align:start
Sometime in the future,

00:21:05.566 --> 00:21:07.267 position:10% line:89% align:start
we will come to face a danger

00:21:07.400 --> 00:21:08.703 position:10% line:89% align:start
that is utterly incomparable

00:21:08.836 --> 00:21:11.606 position:24% line:83% align:start
to anything we have
ever faced before.

00:21:11.739 --> 00:21:12.774 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:21:14.142 --> 00:21:15.475 position:24% line:89% align:start
And that, my dear,

00:21:15.610 --> 00:21:18.246 position:19% line:83% align:start
is the very reason why
you heroes of Earth

00:21:18.378 --> 00:21:19.412 position:27% line:89% align:start
have come to be.

00:21:19.847 --> 00:21:22.183 position:24% line:83% align:start
Although the world
may be free of war,

00:21:22.315 --> 00:21:25.586 position:24% line:83% align:start
