that exists in everyone's heart

00:21:25.720 --> 00:21:28.421 position:21% line:83% align:start
that they do not wish
for anyone else to see.

00:21:28.756 --> 00:21:30.323 position:21% line:89% align:start
No matter who we are,

00:21:30.457 --> 00:21:32.860 position:10% line:89% align:start
that shadow lives within us.

00:21:33.528 --> 00:21:35.462 position:44% line:83% align:start
There
are those who shun the light

00:21:35.596 --> 00:21:38.298 position:24% line:83% align:start
and take advantage
of the dark instead.

00:21:38.465 --> 00:21:39.667 position:44% line:89% align:start
