00:21:40.134 --> 00:21:41.903 position:27% line:89% align:start
understand this.

00:21:42.236 --> 00:21:44.238 position:16% line:89% align:start
The true duty of a hero,

00:21:44.772 --> 00:21:47.708 position:24% line:83% align:start
is to be a shining
beacon of hope for the people

00:21:48.109 --> 00:21:52.046 position:30% line:83% align:start
and, to protect
the very heart of the world.

