dreams of lasting peace.

00:22:11.132 --> 00:22:12.533 position:38% line:89% align:start
This age,

00:22:12.667 --> 00:22:15.102 position:13% line:83% align:start
was a time in human history
when we'd understand

00:22:15.236 --> 00:22:17.404 position:10% line:89% align:start
why the heart mattered most.

00:22:25.445 --> 00:22:27.315 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
An incomparable threat.

00:22:27.447 --> 00:22:29.150 position:19% line:89% align:start
And the duty of heroes.

00:22:29.416 --> 00:22:32.920 position:7% line:83% align:start
